WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.280 --> 00:00:01.160
The Barclays app

2
00:00:01.400 --> 00:00:03.800
How to register on an iOS device

3
00:00:07.680 --> 00:00:09.960
Once you've downloaded the
app from your app store,

4
00:00:10.200 --> 00:00:11.960
it's really easy to get started.

5
00:00:12.880 --> 00:00:14.920
Tap on ‘I already have an account’.

6
00:00:16.280 --> 00:00:19.040
Next you'll need to enter
a 5-digit passcode

7
00:00:19.560 --> 00:00:21.160
and re-enter to confirm.

8
00:00:22.800 --> 00:00:26.880
Read through the Terms & Conditions
and if you're happy, tap to accept them.

9
00:00:27.920 --> 00:00:29.640
If you've not received
an activation code,

10
00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:32.240
tap ‘No, continue without’.

11
00:00:33.720 --> 00:00:38.680
Next, select ‘Barclays UK current
account’ and tap ‘Continue’.

12
00:00:40.520 --> 00:00:43.120
Now, to register, you’ll need
a mobile number,

13
00:00:43.400 --> 00:00:46.240
your Barclays debit card
and your card PIN.

14
00:00:47.560 --> 00:00:49.800
If you have them, tap ‘Continue’.

15
00:00:51.160 --> 00:00:52.440
Tap ‘No’.

16
00:00:53.800 --> 00:00:57.200
You'll then need to enter the 16 digit
number on the front of your card,

17
00:00:59.080 --> 00:01:00.800
before tapping ‘Continue’.

18
00:01:01.680 --> 00:01:04.240
Enter your mobile
number, tap ‘Done’.

19
00:01:06.560 --> 00:01:08.200
Then tap ‘Continue’.

20
00:01:10.360 --> 00:01:12.800
Enter again to confirm and tap ‘Done’,

21
00:01:14.080 --> 00:01:15.520
followed by ‘Continue’.

22
00:01:19.160 --> 00:01:20.920
Once your details have been confirmed,

23
00:01:21.440 --> 00:01:24.160
you'll need to enter your PIN
for the debit card you entered.

24
00:01:26.120 --> 00:01:27.360
Tap ‘Continue’,

25
00:01:28.120 --> 00:01:31.880
then, enter a meaningful word
to welcome you each time you log in,

26
00:01:32.320 --> 00:01:34.440
so you'll know you're
using the genuine app.

27
00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:37.560
Tap ‘Continue’.

28
00:01:39.120 --> 00:01:39.880
And that's it,

29
00:01:40.240 --> 00:01:42.320
your registration will be complete.

30
00:01:43.200 --> 00:01:47.160
You'll now be able to use biometric login
if available on your device,

31
00:01:47.640 --> 00:01:51.440
review your notification preferences
and take a tour of the app.

